title: BRIEF-Lianluo Smart Announces Strategic Cooperation Agreement With Meinian Onehealth Healthcare (Group)
text:
April 16, 2018 / 12:06 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Lianluo Smart Announces Strategic Cooperation Agreement With Meinian Onehealth Healthcare (Group) Reuters Staff 
April 16 (Reuters) - Lianluo Smart Ltd: 
* LIANLUO SMART LIMITED ANNOUNCES STRATEGIC COOPERATION AGREEMENT WITH MEINIAN ONEHEALTH HEALTHCARE (GROUP) CO., LTD. 
* LIANLUO SMART LTD - STRATEGIC COOPERATION AGREEMENT WITH MEINIAN ONEHEALTH HEALTHCARE (GROUP) CO 
* LIANLUO SMART LTD - CO’S SLEEP RESPIRATORY MONITORING PROGRAM HAS BEEN INCLUDED IN MEINIAN ONEHEALTH’S GROUP AND INDIVIDUAL CHECK-UP PACKAGES Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
